WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.220 --> 00:00:03.170
Do you know what the best part is, of running for your life from a horde of

00:00:03.170 --> 00:00:09.704
zombies? Hearing them scream so they don't sneak up on you. Sound is really the

00:00:09.704 --> 00:00:15.479
crucial part of any game. It's the immersive glue that ties together the user

00:00:15.479 --> 00:00:20.219
and their world. And in this unit, we're going to be looking at how you can use

00:00:20.219 --> 00:00:24.090
audio api's for the web to make your games really stand out.

